\">UPC:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">810131704353</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD PANNING KIT: Develop gold panning skills and techniques with the ASR Outdoor x Bobby Bo 10lbs Paydirt Kit! While the paydirt is intended for practicing gold panning skills at home, this kit includes useful gold prospecting equipment that can later be taken to the field for processing unclassified raw materials</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">10LBS GOLD PAYDIRT: 10lb bag of Bobby Bo unclassified paydirt ranks between intermediate and advanced paydirt for the more experienced prospector; paydirt features fine gold, large gravels and significant amounts of black sand that will require classification work</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">5 GALLON BUCKET: Heavy duty plastic bucket with carry handle works in conjunction with large classifier screens; stack sifting screens on top of bucket to create a seamless material classification system, ideal for removing unwanted material from paydirt concentrate</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD PANS: 10 and 12 inch dual riffle gold pans have shallow and deep riffles for processing various kinds of material in one pan; pre-seasoned 10 inch pan is ideal for cleanup of concentrates; large pre-seasoned 14 inch prospecting pan is best suited for processing large amounts of raw material in the field</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PROSPECTING TOOLS: Recovery equipment includes snuffer bottles, glass vials, magnifying tweezers, pipettes, 8lb magnetic separator tool, 10x eye loupe, prospecting scoop, folding shovel, testing stone and 1/8, 1/4 and 1/20 classifier screens</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor 24pc Gold Panning Kit, 5 Gallon Bucket, 10lb Bobby Bo Paydirt, Black</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">349.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>For the gold prospector, novice or veteran, who wants to continue to practice their gold panning skills, look no further than the ASR Outdoor 24pc Gold Panning Kit with 5 Gallon Bucket and 10lbs Bobby Bo Paydirt. \n\nWith a focus on gold panning specifically, the 10lb bag of intermediate to advanced paydirt is a surefire way to develop and enhance gold panning skills and techniques, as well as classification work, without requiring a trip to a claim site. That being said, all the gold prospecting equipment included in this gold panning kit are valuable and useful tools, which can be used time and time again for processing, collection, examination and storage of found gold or other valuable items in the field come future gold prospecting excursions.\n\nThe 10lb bag of ASR Outdoor x Bobby Bo unclassified paydirt ranks on the intermediate and advanced paydirt scale, curated for the more experienced prospector. This paydirt features fine gold for a more difficult extraction process, large gravels and significant amounts of black sand that will require classification work. \n\nThis gold panning kit comes with the following gold prospecting equipment: 10 and 12 inch dual riffles pans (need to be seasoned before use), 10 inch preseasoned finishing pan, 14 preseasoned inch prospecting pan, 5 gallon bucket, classifier screens (1/2, 1/4 and 1/8 inch), snuffer bottles, glass storage vials, magnifying tweezers, pipettes, 8lb magnetic separator tool, 10x eye loupe, prospecting scoop, folding shovel and testing stone.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t</div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t</div> <!-- /container -->\n\t<div style=\"clear:both\">\n\t\t<table>&nbsp;</table>\n\t</div>\n</body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.html#third-party-listing-tools\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=0 width=88 height=33 src=\"https://secureimages.channeladvisor.com/images/channeladvisor/channeladvisor_poweredby-en.gif\"></a></center>",
